{"type":"message","id":"f7da15e1","parentId":"cdfa0f54","timestamp":"2026-03-20T05:02:32.883Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Hmm, the message tool doesn't have an \"info\" action. Let me try a different approach. Let me try to use the im get_messages to see if I can get any info about the chat, or try to search for messages in this chat to see participants.\n\nActually, I don't have a direct tool to list group members. Let me check what tools I have available... \n\nLooking at my tools:\n- feishu_im_user_get_messages - gets messages from a chat\n- feishu_im_user_get_thread_messages - gets thread messages\n- feishu_im_user_search_messages - search messages\n- feishu_search_user - search users\n\nI could try to get messages from this chat to see who has sent messages, but that's not a direct group member list.\n\nLet me try getting messages from this chat to at least see who's been active.","thinkingSignature":"cf4bea75cecd1f8c1a56b5a3585675c33b9cfe23c1bd6f67775dd0ad9bb99e5e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gcwnxd7zaryi_1","name":"feishu_im_user_get_messages","arguments":{"chat_id":"oc_a949c497b892cfdc68e131dcfdc066bb","page_size":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":4116,"output":234,"cacheRead":31674,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36024,"cost":{"input":0.0012347999999999999,"output":0.0002808,"cacheRead":0.0009502199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0024658199999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773982936737}}
{"type":"message","id":"2ed6fd74","parentId":"f7da15e1","timestamp":"2026-03-20T05:02:34.157Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_gcwnxd7zaryi_1","toolName":"feishu_im_user_get_messages","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"messages\": [\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54f902840ca4b349a7227922a55\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"需要您再次授权一下，授权完成后我就能查看群成员信息~\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a9366de690795bd3\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T13:01:56+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b54f905b594a0b4c20d57f6f8c71\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54f902d068a8b288d4ff4c87bbc\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"interactive\",\n      \"content\": \"<card title=\\\"授权成功\\\">\\nFeishu account authorized. Continuing with your request.\\n\\nLet me know if you ever need to revoke the permissions.\\n</card>\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a9366de690795bd3\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T13:01:54+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b54f905b594a0b4c20d57f6f8c71\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54f905b594a0b4c20d57f6f8c71\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"你能查看群成员吗@大聪明\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_36fee30f31f267e7dcb6e16b3b4a2275\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T13:01:43+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"mentions\": [\n        {\n          \"key\": \"@_user_1\",\n          \"id\": \"ou_a61ab492fc459830d4cae5b5c55b58e4\",\n          \"name\": \"大聪明\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54f9061894a0b3f9d9e7cf5a2b3\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"找到董事长了！不过抱歉，目前我的工具箱暂时没有添加群成员的功能权限 😅\\n您可以手动在飞书群里点击「邀请成员」把王杭加进来，或者如果有管理员权限可以在飞书管理后台操作。\\n需要我帮您做别的吗？\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a9366de690795bd3\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T13:01:01+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b54f909e6fca4b103f999c8de606\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54f906c838a8b49ca60f0d4e4a5\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"董事长，需要您先授权一下获取您的飞书信息。授权完成后我再帮您入群哦~\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a9366de690795bd3\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T13:00:48+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b54f909e6fca4b103f999c8de606\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54f909156cb4b3bf091408c678c\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"interactive\",\n      \"content\": \"<card title=\\\"授权成功\\\">\\nFeishu account authorized. Continuing with your request.\\n\\nLet me know if you ever need to revoke the permissions.\\n</card>\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a9366de690795bd3\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T13:00:45+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b54f909e6fca4b103f999c8de606\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54f909e6fca4b103f999c8de606\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"我说你的[USER.md](http://user.md/) - 我服务的对象 加入本群的群组成员@大聪明\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_36fee30f31f267e7dcb6e16b3b4a2275\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T13:00:34+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"mentions\": [\n        {\n          \"key\": \"@_user_1\",\n          \"id\": \"ou_a61ab492fc459830d4cae5b5c55b58e4\",\n          \"name\": \"大聪明\"\n  