{"type":"message","id":"765ac105","parentId":"7e833894","timestamp":"2026-03-20T05:04:04.944Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking what it would take for me to see other group members. Let me think about this - I need to check if there's a Feishu API that can list group members. Looking at my available tools, I don't see a direct \"get group members\" function.\n\nHowever, let me check the documentation or see if there's a way through the im (instant messaging) APIs. The feishu_im_user_get_messages just gets messages, not members.\n\nLooking at my tools again:\n- feishu_im_user_get_messages - get messages\n- feishu_im_user_get_thread_messages - get thread messages\n- feishu_im_user_search_messages - search messages\n- feishu_im_user_message - send messages\n- feishu_im_user_fetch_resource - download files/images\n- feishu_im_bot_image - download as bot\n\nNone of these are for listing group members. \n\nThere might be a different API endpoint for group members, but it's not in my current toolset. I should be honest with the user about this limitation.\n\nActually, let me think - is there any way? Perhaps through the contact or core APIs? Looking at my tools, I don't see any contact-related APIs either.\n\nThe user might need to either:\n1. Grant additional permissions/scopes to the OpenClaw app\n2. Use a different approach\n3. Check if there's a way to enable this functionality\n\nI should explain this limitation honestly.","thinkingSignature":"e8054c9193d6951c76307499420e9639e53f20fbe64e11883b42890e275ac32c"},{"type":"text","text":"目前我的工具箱里没有群成员列表的 API 权限。要解锁这个功能，可能需要：\n\n1. **扩展飞书应用权限** - 需要在飞书开放平台给应用添加 `im:chat:members` 相关的权限 scope\n2. **更新工具集** - 让开发者给我添加工具来查询群成员\n\n简单说，不是做不到，是权限没开~ 😅\n\n如果您是管理员或开发者，可以去飞书开放平台看看应用权限配置。需要我帮您做什么别的吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":147,"output":403,"cacheRead":35190,"cacheWrite":2994,"totalTokens":38734,"cost":{"input":0