{"type":"message","id":"e6bf0431","parentId":"61b09a3d","timestamp":"2026-03-20T05:15:03.836Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The tab seems to have issues. Let me try to look for other approaches - maybe I can find APIs or SDKs that I could use to generate videos. But realistically, most AI video generation platforms require:\n1. Paid accounts\n2. Manual login/operations\n3. API keys\n\nLet me be honest with the user about the limitations and suggest practical alternatives.","thinkingSignature":"cf14c4253a48dbc24f66c0759d48ca08d68b452b7b95672e12205fce32e82a4b"},{"type":"text","text":"董事长，我研究了一圈，发现一个现实问题：\n\n**目前AI视频生成的困境：**\n- 🚫 **都需要付费账号** - Runway、Pika、RunwayML、Kaiber 等都要充钱\n- 🚫 **没有免费开放的API** - 不能让我直接调用生成视频\n- 🚫 **需要人脸识别/验证码** - 手动注册登录\n\n**实际可行的方案：**\n\n| 方案 | 成本 | 可操作性 |\n|-----|------|---------|\n| 1. 买现成素材剪辑 | 低（几十块/月） | ✅ 我能配合写文案+配音 |\n| 2. 找我做图文号 | 0 | ✅ 纯文字+配音就能发 |\n| 3. 你提供视频AI账号 | 你付费 | ✅ 我帮你操作 |\n\n**我的建议：**\n先做**抖音图文号**（我写文案+配语音，你配图发），跑通后再投钱做视频。\n\n或者，您愿意投点钱买视频素材会员吗？我来负责剪辑制作~ 🎬"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":22607,"output":293,"cacheRead":31674,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54574,"cost":{"input":0.0067821,"output":0.0003516,"cacheRead":0.0009502199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00808392}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773983683144}}
{"type":"message","id":"47e08c2e","parentId":"e6bf0431","timestamp":"2026-03-20T05:16:26.345Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-20 13:16:25 GMT+8] Feishu[dacm] group oc_a949c497b892cfdc68e131dcfdc066bb | ou_36fee30f31f267e7dcb6e16b3b4a2275 [msg:om_x100b54f9cc4bf0b0b3469c189e8e0d4, @bot]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54f9cc4bf0b0b3469c189e8e0d4\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_36fee30f31f267e7dcb6e16b3b4a2275\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_a949c497b892cfdc68e131dcfdc066bb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_36fee30f31f267e7dcb6e16b3b4a2275\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-03-20 13:16 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_a949c497b892cfdc68e131dcfdc066bb\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_36fee30f31f267e7dcb6e16b3b4a2275\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_36fee30f31f267e7dcb6e16b3b4a2275\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_36fee30f31f267e7dcb6e16b3b4a2275\"\n}\n```\n\n这些是国内的吗 怎么又的我登陆不上去"}],"timestamp":1773983786343}}
{"type":"message","id":"42a70ff5","parentId":"47e08c2e","timestamp":"2026-03-20T05:16:38.007Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking why some of these are not domestic (Chinese) platforms and why some I can't log in to.\n\nLet me explain - Pika.art and Runway are US-based platforms, not Chinese. They may have access restrictions from China or require VPN.\n\nLet me suggest Chinese AI video platforms instead that might work better:\n- 剪映 (Jianying) - by ByteDance\n- 快影 (Kuaishou)\n- 腾讯智影 (Tencent Zhipian)\n- 百度AIGC tools\n- 必剪 (Bilibili)\n\nBut the fundamental issue remains - these all require user accounts and payments. I don't have direct API access to generate videos.\n\nLet me be honest with the user about the technical limitations.","thinkingSignature":"78e8de469f492bc60518251ff877f5b31c36537d70bf00262e9f674b6c258b76"},{"type":"text","text":"抱歉董事长！\n\n刚才看的是**国外的平台**（Pika是美国，Runway是美国），国内访问受限或者要翻墙。\n\n**国内的AI视频平台：**\n- 剪映（字节跳动）\n- 快影（快手）\n- 腾讯智影\n- 百度AIGC\n\n**问题是：**\n这些平台**都需要用户自己登录账号**，我不能代注册也不能直接调用API生成。\n\n**核心瓶颈：**\n我做不了视频生成的底层操作，只因我的工具箱里没有视频生成API。\n\n---\n\n**换个思路：**\n\n董事长，如果您愿意**每年花几百块**买素材网站会员（如新片场、视觉中国），我可以帮您：\n1. 选好素材片段\n2. 写好配音稿\n3. 做好初步剪辑\n\n您愿意投资这个成本吗？💰"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":147,"output":326,"cacheRead":52000,"cacheWrite":2639,"totalTokens":55112,"cost":{"input":0.0000441,"output":0.00039119999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0015599999999999998,"cacheWrite":0.00031667999999999996,"total":0.00231198}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773983786344}}
