{"type":"message","id":"9a0c184a","parentId":"80af1355","timestamp":"2026-03-20T05:23:29.834Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The interface doesn't seem to be responding well to my clicks. Let me try a different approach - I see there's a tooltip showing the points with a \"领取\" button next to \"签到打卡\". Let me try to find and click that. Looking at the snapshot, I can see the tooltip with the check-in option. The button \"领取\" should be clickable. Let me try to look for a different reference or just try clicking on different parts of the interface.\n\nActually, wait - the issue might be that the tooltip is showing but I need to click on a specific button inside it. Looking at the snapshot more carefully:\n- There's \"+20\" next to \"签到打卡\" \n- There's a \"领取\" button\n\nBut my click doesn't seem to be working. The browser automation might not be able to interact well with these tooltip elements.\n\nLet me tell the user the situation - I can see the check-in button but can't click it through automation. Maybe they need to do it manually, or we need to find another way.","thinkingSignature":"8a995aa0f5f3d5e1881294ed96a74a89b1e19ceea337e92fa547e4468c35b0a5"},{"type":"text","text":"董事长不好意思，这个签到弹窗我操作不了，可能是网页限制。\n\n**您手动操作一下：**\n1. 点右上角「我的积分」\n2. 点「签到打卡」旁边的「领取」\n3. 领完20积分告诉我\n\n或者您去**百度APP**签到也能得积分，然后同步过来。\n\n您先搞一下积分，弄好了我再帮您生成视频！🎬"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":77188,"output":296,"cacheRead":31674,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":109158,"cost":{"input":0.0231564,"output":0.00035519999999999996,"cacheRead":0.0009502199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.024461820000000002}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773984201367}}
