{"type":"message","id":"3d8b27e0","parentId":"ed84d34b","timestamp":"2026-03-20T05:28:37.448Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The click didn't seem to do anything visible. Let me try a different approach - maybe I can find the video download URL through the page source or try to get it via the network. But that might be too complex.\n\nLet me check if there are any buttons I'm missing in the UI. The video has an image thumbnail but I don't see a download button in the snapshot. \n\nMaybe I can try right-clicking or looking for more options. Let me try to see if there's a context menu or additional options when I click on the video.\n\nActually, let me try using the exec tool to download the video using curl if I can find the video URL. Or I can try using the browser's developer tools to find the video source.\n\nBut this is getting complex. Let me just tell the user the situation and suggest the easiest way - using the APP to download.","thinkingSignature":"c393fa88846c59bf4f6b1176904324ef89a18365f4473d936e54b699074d9f78"},{"type":"text","text":"董事长，网页版度加的下载按钮藏得比较深。让我试试用另一种方式：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_w20n4mqi3eue_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"powershell -Command \"Get-Process | Where-Object {$_.MainWindowTitle -like '*度加*'} | Select-Object Id,ProcessName,MainWindowTitle\"","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":75456,"output":262,"cacheRead":31674,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":107392,"cost":{"input":0.0226368,"output":0.0003144,"cacheRead":0.0009502199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02390142}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773984509390}}
