{"type":"message","id":"d413f926","parentId":"e4e9bf77","timestamp":"2026-03-20T05:28:51.332Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"PowerShell encoding issue. Let me just tell the user the simplest way to download - use the APP.\n\nThe simplest solution now is: the user should download the video from the DuJia APP on their phone. This is the most reliable way.","thinkingSignature":"e2c9ba8b3b8c430442354a6d1b8c531fce8c4ea216f57a4526b71ba0e580f83c"},{"type":"text","text":"董事长，网页版确实没有直接的下载按钮。\n\n**最简单的办法：用度加APP下载**\n\n1. 打开**度加APP** → 「我的作品」\n2. 点击刚才生成的视频\n3. 点「导出」或「下载」\n\n或者您直接在那边的网页上点击视频，看看能不能播放+下载。\n\n您先试试能不能下载？我这边继续研究有没有别的办法~ 📱"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":90523,"output":135,"cacheRead":31674,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":122332,"cost":{"input":0.027156899999999998,"output":0.00016199999999999998,"cacheRead":0.0009502199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.028269119999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773984520686}}
