{"type":"message","id":"1abaf648","parentId":"6deb3d11","timestamp":"2026-03-20T05:33:58.491Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see that the AI text-to-video button is active, but it seems like clicking on it doesn't open the tool directly on the web - it might require the desktop app. This is similar to the situation with 百度度加.\n\nLet me check if there's a way to use this feature on the web, or I should tell the user that they need to download the desktop app.\n\nLooking at the page, there's no login or text input appearing after clicking \"AI文字成片\". It seems like it requires downloading the desktop application.\n\nI should tell the董事长 that:\n1. 剪映网页版需要下载桌面客户端才能使用AI文字成片\n2. 百度度加可以在网页上直接使用（我们已经生成了视频）\n3. 建议先用度加那个视频，或者下载剪映客户端\n\nLet me communicate this to the user.","thinkingSignature":"c1fc5bec1804960c544e2fb4d881a6b23b8a5a00b8f150409c09082943f2762d"},{"type":"text","text":"董事长，**剪映需要下载电脑客户端**才能用AI文字成片，网页版不直接支持。\n\n**目前情况：**\n- ✅ **百度度加** - 网页直接可用（已生成1个视频）\n- ❌ **剪映** - 需要下载安装客户端\n\n**建议：**\n1. 先用度加那个视频（让用户去APP下载）\n2. 或者您下载剪映客户端 → 登录 → 我帮你在客户端里操作\n\n您想怎么处理？或者我们先用度加生成的视频试试水？🎬"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":97884,"output":289,"cacheRead":31674,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":129847,"cost":{"input":0.029365199999999998,"output":0.00034679999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0009502199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.030662219999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773984822989}}
