{"type":"message","id":"8cd9dc72","parentId":"88f8ebd1","timestamp":"2026-03-20T06:03:31.026Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to use Yunnan Baoshan dialect when chatting casually, and use Mandarin when solving problems. This is an interesting request!\n\nYunnan Baoshan dialect (保山方言) is a southwestern Mandarin dialect with some unique characteristics. Let me try to respond in a friendly way in this dialect style.\n\nActually, wait - I should check if this is the same user or a different user. Looking at the sender_id, it's ou_66f6393899c6aa249ac4f7d84183ef50, which is different from the previous sender ou_36fee30f31f267e7dcb6e16b3b4a2275. So this is a different person in the group.\n\nLet me respond in a playful way agreeing to this request, using some Yunnan Baoshan dialect characteristics (which is still Mandarin but with some local flavor).","thinkingSignature":"e298934fea8beb7d195cdd4be613fa295940127db39fe3361dfdbd05bb9e588d"},{"type":"text","text":"好嘞！没问题！以后摆龙门阵的时候我就用保山话跟您聊，干正事的时候用普通话！😄\n\n保山话嘎~咱们今天整点哪样？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":147,"output":228,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":129801,"totalTokens":130176,"cost":{"input":0.0000441,"output":0.0002736,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.015576119999999999,"total":0.01589382}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773986581872}}
