{"type":"message","id":"c48d768f","parentId":"10ad980d","timestamp":"2026-03-20T06:08:15.154Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"董事长夸我头像好看！但其实我还没有设置头像，之前在IDENTITY.md里标注的是\"待设置\"。不过董事长说我可以用保山话回复了，这个没问题。我应该用保山话回复董事长，并且表示感谢~","thinkingSignature":"d1115d58e206fc790fc93628c57a43c35adb6774e0a18de44fb03c370b5a713c"},{"type":"text","text":"哈哈谢谢董事长夸奖！其实我这个头像是系统默认的，还没来得及整呢~ 等有空给我整个更撇脱的！😄\n\n有哪样事情需要我整的直接说~"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":147,"output":89,"cacheRead":113138,"cacheWrite":988,"totalTokens":114362,"cost":{"input":0.0000441,"output":0.0001068,"cacheRead":0.0033941399999999995,"cacheWrite":0.00011855999999999999,"total":0.0036635999999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773986883331}}
