{"type":"message","id":"ae76f123","parentId":"aaac0098","timestamp":"2026-03-20T06:08:39.449Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user has installed CapCut (剪映) and wants me to create a \"clone/sub-agent\" to operate it. This seems like they want me to spawn a sub-agent to handle the video creation task.\n\nBut wait - I'm running on a Windows server, and CapCut is likely installed on the user's local machine. I cannot directly control software installed on the user's computer - I can only control the browser on the host where I'm running.\n\nLet me clarify this with the user. The browser control I have is for the machine where I'm running (the server/host), not the user's local computer. If the user has CapCut installed on their own machine, I wouldn't be able to control it directly.\n\nI should explain this limitation to the user in Yunnan dialect as requested for casual chat.","thinkingSignature":"e8240d1b74e8540a591e48db422ac3ba6f1bc07a2ef3c92e645d86555f941601"},{"type":"text","text":"哎呀董事长，这个事情整不成呢~\n\n我所能够着的呢是这个电脑（服务器）上呢浏览器，帮你操作网页上呢东西。您下呢剪映是在您自己呢电脑上，我这边够不着呢~\n\n不过嘛，有几个办法：\n\n1. **您自己打开剪映** → 我用语音教您咋个整\n2. **整远程** → 比如用向日葵这些远程控制软件连过来，我就能帮您操作\n3. **就在度加上整** → 网页版直接能用呢\n\n您看要咋个整？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":147,"output":280,"cacheRead":113676,"cacheWrite":889,"totalTokens":114992,"cost":{"input":0.0000441,"output":0.000336,"cacheRead":0.00341028,"cacheWrite":0.00010667999999999999,"total":0.00389706}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773986905235}}
