{"type":"message","id":"8ac1b32e","parentId":"13bb57a5","timestamp":"2026-03-20T06:23:42.071Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking why I can't use web search. Let me explain - my web search tool needs a Brave API key which is not configured. I should explain this in a simple way.","thinkingSignature":"8e49d34c52a047bf49d904c35590923c97927bd0a2ced1d9763089792772bbb4"},{"type":"text","text":"董事长，是这样呢——\n\n我呢网上搜索功能需要配置一个搜索API密匙（ Brave Search API key），现在呢没配置上，所以搜不了东西。\n\n不过嘛，我脑子里记得很多东西呢，一般呢问题都能答得上來。只是刚才给您找小说这种呢，需要网上搜最新呢信息，我就有点抓瞎了~\n\n下次我叫开发者帮我把搜索功能整好，那样就能更快更准了呢！\n\n还有哪样要问呢？😄"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":147,"output":135,"cacheRead":123548,"cacheWrite":1234,"totalTokens":125064,"cost":{"input":0.0000441,"output":0.00016199999999999998,"cacheRead":0.0037064399999999996,"cacheWrite":0.00014807999999999998,"total":0.00406062}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773987812312}}
