{"type":"message","id":"a4b74cfc","parentId":"f1023b9d","timestamp":"2026-03-20T06:26:19.816Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Great! I was able to search using Bing. I found some good results. Let me summarize for the user in Yunnan dialect.","thinkingSignature":"bdeb03db68fe36891d0372e2ab396d1ca38bd614da7b98481918c6fa0a09dd03"},{"type":"text","text":"董事长！搜到了！不用API也能搜呢！\n\n给您找到几本好书：\n\n---\n\n**📚 推荐书单：**\n\n1. **《契诃夫短篇小说集》** - 豆瓣9.2分！经典中的经典\n2. **《马克·吐温短篇小说集》** - 《百万英镑》就是这里呢\n3. **《欧亨利短篇小说集》** - 《麦琪的礼物》《最后一片叶子》\n4. **《莫泊桑短篇小说集》** - 《项链》《羊脂球》\n\n**一套搞定呢：**\n- 《世界四大短篇小说集》（全4册） - 京东/当当都有，一套全部搞定\n\n这几本都是幽默讽刺、讽刺生活呢调调，跟契诃夫呢风格差不多！\n\n您想要哪一本？我帮您看看哪里有卖~📕"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":111352,"output":210,"cacheRead":31674,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":143236,"cost":{"input":0.0334056,"output":0.000252,"cacheRead":0.0009502199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.034607820000000004}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773987961504}}
