{"type":"message","id":"3d32930f","parentId":"841d898a","timestamp":"2026-03-20T06:32:08.760Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to open CapCut (剪映) on the desktop. But I already checked - this is the server's desktop, not the user's local computer. CapCut is not installed on this server. \n\nThe desktop contents show:\n- StarOffice folder\n- Some Chinese folders (icons and downloads)\n- 360 Security shortcuts\n- Google Chrome\n- Microsoft Edge\n- CapCut (剪映) - this is actually shown as \"剪映专业版.lnk\"\n\nWait, I see \"剪映专业版.lnk\" in the list! Let me check again. Yes, there's a file called \"剪映专业版.lnk\" - that's CapCut Pro!\n\nBut even if I can find the shortcut, the issue is this is the SERVER's desktop, not the user's local computer. The user is probably thinking I can control their local machine, but I can only control this server.\n\nLet me explain this to the user again - this server doesn't have CapCut installed, and even if it did, it wouldn't be the same as the CapCut on their local computer.","thinkingSignature":"82ff35150046003896ba7daf5092f377905fbfc879f2072b3ffe41b07dd184fe"},{"type":"text","text":"董事长，我刚才看呢是我们这个服务器呢桌面，不是您本地呢电脑。这个服务器上确实有剪映呢快捷方式，但：\n\n1. 这是**服务器上**呢剪映\n2. 您本地呢剪映是安装在您自己呢电脑上呢\n\n两个不一样呢~\n\n不过服务器上呢剪映我也能帮您打开！让我试试：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_q6igjpubcqrf_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"powershell -Command \"Start-Process 'C:\\Users\\Administrator\\Desktop\\剪映专业版.lnk'\"","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":159,"output":353,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":115836,"totalTokens":116348,"cost":{"input":0.0000477,"output":0.0004236,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.013900319999999999,"total":0.014371619999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773988304092}}
