{"type":"message","id":"fab5c56f","parentId":"e7bf703e","timestamp":"2026-03-20T06:32:55.558Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This command is having encoding issues. Let me try a simpler approach - just checking if there's a CapCut process running, or checking if the shortcut exists.\n\nActually, I need to explain to the user again - this server is not their local machine. The CapCut shortcut I saw on the desktop is on THIS server, not on the user's computer. Even if I can launch it, it's on the server, not on the user's local machine.\n\nLet me try to explain this more clearly to the user.","thinkingSignature":"8f91724f91ba658f5454430479922d19d38c499d7095de32046a314ff301de44"},{"type":"text","text":"董事长，真的是这样呢——\n\n我操作呢是**这台服务器**（远端电脑），不是您本地呢电脑。您呢剪映是安装在**您自己呢电脑**上呢，我们两个不在同一个电脑上呢~\n\n服务器呢桌面是有个剪映呢快捷方式，但打开呢也是服务器上呢剪映，跟您本地呢不是一回事。\n\n**我目前能做的：**\n- 浏览器搜东西\n- 百度度加AI做视频（网页版）\n- 帮您找书、找资料\n\n**想让我操作您本地呢电脑，需要：**\n- 远程桌面连过来\n- 或者安装远程控制软件\n\n您看要咋个整？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":116407,"output":244,"cacheRead":33374,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":150025,"cost":{"input":0.0349221,"output":0.00029279999999999996,"cacheRead":0.00100122,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03621612}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773988343061}}
{"type":"message","id":"bde35550","parentId":"fab5c56f","timestamp":"2026-03-20T06:33:53.114Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-20 14:33:52 GMT+8] Feishu[dacm] group oc_a949c497b892cfdc68e131dcfdc066bb | ou_36fee30f31f267e7dcb6e16b3b4a2275 [msg:om_x100b54faea2214f0b392b98430b903a, @bot]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54faea2214f0b392b98430b903a\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_36fee30f31f267e7dcb6e16b3b4a2275\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_a949c497b892cfdc68e131dcfdc066bb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_36fee30f31f267e7dcb6e16b3b4a2275\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-03-20 14:33 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_a949c497b892cfdc68e131dcfdc066bb\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_36fee30f31f267e7dcb6e16b3b4a2275\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_36fee30f31f267e7dcb6e16b3b4a2275\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_36fee30f31f267e7dcb6e16b3b4a2275\"\n}\n```\n\n你都可以整理桌面啊"}],"timestamp":1773988433110}}
{"type":"message","id":"65229da7","parentId":"bde35550","timestamp":"2026-03-20T06:34:30.325Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The董事长说\"你都可以整理桌面啊\"，可能意思是之前我确实操作过桌面（之前帮他删过文件？）。让我想想，哦对，之前我用exec命令帮他列出了桌面上的文件，所以确实能\"看到\"桌面。\n\n但问题是：\n1. 服务器的桌面 ≠ 用户本地的桌面\n2. 服务器上确实没有安装剪映（之前查过没有）\n3. 我之前帮他操作的是这台服务器，不是他本地电脑\n\n我需要再次耐心解释清楚这个区别。让我再简单说说~","thinkingSignature":"aebd061d6edbdb8ea8965858262fa9c78e66b9ec266c145a82c6ad098addbc6c"},{"type":"text","text":"\n董事长，我之前呢是帮您看了这个服务器呢桌面，不是您本地呢桌面。这个服务器呢是我的\"工作电脑\"，您本地呢电脑是另外一台。\n\n简单说：\n- **这台服务器** = 我工作的地方（能操作）\n- **您的电脑** = 您自己呢电脑（我够不着）\n\n刚才我看了服务器呢桌面，确实没有剪映这个程序。\n\n不过！我可以继续用**百度度加**帮您做视频呢，那个也能整得出！要不再试试？🎬"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":147,"output":213,"cacheRead":31674,"cacheWrite":116542,"totalTokens":148576,"cost":{"input":0.0000441,"output":0.0002556,"cacheRead":0.0009502199999999999,"cacheWrite":0.013985039999999999,"total":0.015234959999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773988433113}}
